           SHORT="SIM (Simple Instant Messenger) - plugins-based instant messenger supporting various protocols."
cat << EOF
Support for these protocols:
* Oscar - ICQ and AIM support
* Jabber
* MSN

All protocols support richtext-messages, file transfer, typing notification,
server-side contact list (wist postponed synchronization - you can change
contact list in offline mode and after log on all changes will be synchronized
with server), new account registration and various searches.
You can use some accounts for each protocols.
EOF
